## Description {#details}

An union-find based Minimum Spanning Tree for CFG.

Implements a Union-find algorithm to compute Minimum Spanning Tree for a given CFG.

Definition at line 40 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/transforms/include/llvm/transforms/instrumentation/cfgmst-h">CFGMST.h</a>.
